    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10687902>
    dc:description "FIG. 11. Hirtodrosophila ordinaria, lighter individual (a female). A. Habitus, lateral. B. Head and thorax, dorsal. C. Head and thorax, lateral. D. Abdomen, dorsal." ;
