<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10687958>
    dc:description "FIG. 30. Preliminary scheme of relationships in the Holarctic Hirtodrosophila melanderi species group. Species that are omitted are H. shaitanensis and H. alpiniae (see text)." ;
